as this one in Thailand than to anywhere else outside Southeast Asia. KARI RENE 
HALL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Sovan Un CHRISTINE WALETER / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, San Tran ; Photo, Kheng Bou Los Angeles Times 
</P>
